trans-unit.source: SymbolResolver is an extension for providing a host <xref href="System.Activities.LocationReferenceEnvironment"></xref> containing objects that can be dereferenced by a string name.
trans-unit.target: SymbolResolver è un'estensione per fornire un host <xref href="System.Activities.LocationReferenceEnvironment"> </xref> contenente oggetti che possono essere dereferenziati da un nome di stringa.

trans-unit.source: Values provided through a SymbolResolver are not persisted.
trans-unit.target: Non vengono mantenuti i valori forniti tramite SymbolResolver.

trans-unit.source: Persistence of SymbolResolver values is a host responsibility.
trans-unit.target: Persistenza dei valori di SymbolResolver è responsabilità dell'host.

trans-unit.source: Copies the symbols in the <xref href="System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver"></xref> to an existing one-dimensional array of key/value pairs, starting at the specified array index.
